text: "Which Way Do I Go (Now That I'm Gone)" is a song recorded by American country music artist Waylon Jennings. It was released in January 1989 as the second single from the album Full Circle. The song reached #28 on the Billboard Hot Country Singles & Tracks chart. The song was written by Johnny MacRae and Steve Clark. ==Chart performance== {|class="wikitable sortable" !align="left"|Chart (1989) !align="center"|Peak position |- |} ==References== Category:1989 singles Category:1988 songs Category:Waylon Jennings songs Category:Songs written by Johnny MacRae Category:Song recordings produced by Jimmy Bowen Category:MCA Records singles
